ING OF IODINE CONTENT OF URINE:</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	This process was started from 2003 after setting up proper Iodine Monitoring Laboratory at the Directorate of Health Services. <strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	  This is being done by collecting Urine samples from School Children and tested in the Iodine Laboratory at the Directorate.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4><u></u></h4>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Year</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>No. of sample tested</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Sample below 100 ug/L  </h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Sample above 100 ug/L</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2008-09</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>282</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>282</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>294</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>294</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2010-11</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>233</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>233</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2011-12</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>500</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>500</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2012-13</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td colspan=\"3\">\r\n		<h4>Nil (due to lack of reagent)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2013-14</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>741</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>741</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2014-15 (upto 3<sup>rd</sup> qrtrs)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>1925</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>0</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>1925</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong><strong>GLOBAL IDD DAY:</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	This important day is being observed every year particularly to create Awareness on IDD and importance of Iodized salt by using various Medias.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>GOITRE SURVEY</strong>:\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	A number of surveys on IDD have been carried out since 1978.\r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Year</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>District</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>No. of person examine</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Percentage</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2007-08</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Serchhip (Oct 07)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>3305</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>16.1%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Aizawl (Apr 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>9901</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>17.1%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Saiha (May 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>6240</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>13.6%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Lunglei (Jul 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>6074</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>14.7%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Lawngtlai (Aug 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>7398</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>12.3%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Mamit (Sep 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2653</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>20.3%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Kolasib (Oct 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2227</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>13.2%</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2009-10</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>Champhai (Nov 09)</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	<td>\r\n		<h4>2022</h4>\r\n	</td>\r\n	